  "title": "Architectural Coordinator (BCA CONQUAS, BIM software/Autodesk Revit)",
  "description": "<p><em>Our client is a leading construction company, specialize in marine engineering and land reclamation projects.</em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee BIM modelers to create shop drawings.</li>\n  <li>Manage schedule for shop drawing preparation/approval and material approval/procurement based on master programme and monitor the status.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with BIM team on drawings production to identify conflicts with other trades.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with Consultants and Subcontractors to identify the Architectural construction details and M&amp;E services.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Architectural or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 4 years of <strong>building projects</strong> experience in <strong>Hospital/Medical Facilities.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge in <strong>Singapore Building Codes, BCA CONQUAS </strong>and <strong>Quality Mark Assessment.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
